git vtag [<options>] [--] [<commit>...] - Compute next vtag.

    -h|--help               display help
    -u|--reuse              reuse most recent vtag (move it to current branch tip)
    --alpha                 switch to alpha pre-release
    --beta                  switch to beta pre-release
    --rc                    switch to rc pre-release
    --rtm                   switch to rtm (remove pre-release)
    <commit>...             commit on which vtag is computed (default to HEAD)
    
example:
    git vtag --alpha | xarg git newtag
